{"tid":1767843,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"擊退支那人返上大灣區","createTime":"2019-12-03T15:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T15:51:26.000Z","uid":207977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f953406e4f7736114bb26606d6e63c4ef85fea6a","tid":1767843,"uid":207977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:10:28.000Z","msg":"屯門牛，要蘇醒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一田減價已經令支那人無懼繼續落黎<br />\n既然佢地禁撚鐘意落<br />\n我地係各個旅遊巴，落客區咁樣迎接佢地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcDVZJ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcDVZJ5.jpg&h=d74a714a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n令佢地開車調頭返上大灣區<br />\n就算唔咁都搞返個去屯門公園和你tea，<br />\n支那大媽禁撚鐘意唱歌，<br />\n我地係佢地隔離唱「願榮光歸香港」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屯門又出現返大量支那人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1760277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1760277</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8a098e7dc0b125bcf522878b5e01518788ead14","tid":1767843,"uid":207977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"Push 呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d658a018547e7621d283c62f1cebe1af7941ad","tid":1767843,"uid":278990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T15:51:26.000Z","msg":"多到仆街"}]}